  "detailed_description": "<h1>Resident Evil Re:Verse</h1><p>IMPORTANT NOTICE: Service for Resident Evil Re:Verse will end on June 29, 2025. The game will no longer be playable from this date. Resident Evil Re:Verse and all related DLC will be removed from distribution on March 3, 2025.\r\nDetails of the operational period for Resident Evil Re:Verse, including commencement of availability and any potential announcements relating to the end of service, can be found on the official website.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Beloved Resident Evil characters clash in a fight to the death!\r\n\r\nTest your skills against other players in six-person deathmatch battles.\r\n\r\nBut don't forget the terrifying creatures! You'll need to master the skills of the heroes and creatures alike if you want to claw your way to victory!\r\n\r\nNote: A Capcom ID is required in order to play.",
  "about_the_game": "Beloved Resident Evil characters clash in a fight to the death!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTest your skills against other players in six-person deathmatch battles.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBut don't forget the terrifying creatures! You'll need to master the skills of the heroes and creatures alike if you want to claw your way to victory!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote: A Capcom ID is required in order to play.",
